6.1. The Client undertakes to:
— Ensure free access to the site at the agreed times;
— Provide the necessary administrative authorisations (planning permission, prior declaration, co-ownership agreement, etc.);
— Report any element likely to affect the smooth progress of the works (presence of asbestos, lead, buried pipes, etc.);
— Protect or remove moveable property and valuables located in the work area.

6.2. The Client has a right of withdrawal of fourteen (14) days from signature of the quote where it was concluded off-premises (at the Client's home), in accordance with Articles L.221-18 et seq. of the French Consumer Code. This right of withdrawal does not apply if the works have begun before the expiry of this period with the Client's express consent.
